title: ALL ACCESS: Canelo vs. Plant | Ep. 1 | SHOWTIME PPV
author: SHOWTIME Sports
description:
ALL ACCESS: CANELO VS. PLANT episode 1 brings viewers behind-the-scenes as unified WBA/WBC/WBO Super Middleweight World Champion Canelo Alvarez and IBF Super Middleweight World Champion Caleb Plant prepare for one of the biggest and most important fights of 2021.

The two stars battle in a SHOWTIME PPV event on Saturday, November 6th at 9pm ET/6PM PT.

#SHOSports #AllAccess #CaneloPlant #CaneloAlvarez #CalebPlant
